            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="43183615">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">对『胡索维亚努斯』作品的描述： 冷僻而博学，精准而奇异，庄严又琐碎</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-04-17 23:02</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <p>对『胡索维亚努斯』作品的描述：</p><p>冷僻而博学，精准而奇异，庄严又琐碎</p>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
